
* Docker directo:
    - docker run --rm -p 3000:3000 -ti -v /Users/jaime.henao/arheanja/Backstage-solutions/backstage-app:/app -w /app node:18-bookworm-slim bash

    - docker run --rm -p 3000:3000 -ti -v /Users/jaime.henao/arheanja/Backstage-solutions/backstage-app:/app -w /app node:20-bullseye bash

* Dockerfile y docker-compose.yml:

    1. Construir la imagen:

     - docker-compose build    

    2. Levantar el contenedor:

     - docker-compose up -d

    3. Entrar al contenedor:

     - docker exec -it backstage-app bash
    
    4. eliminar contenedor:

     - docker-compose down

* Backstage dentro del contenedor:

    - npx @backstage/create-app@latest

    - yarn install

    - yarn dev